talent level 10 Upgrade Molten Steel
increase magic resist gain by 20%
increase pure resist gain by 25%
increase armor lost by 0.4
increase pure damage taken by 1%
increase radius scaling by 45%
reduce mana cost per seconds by 4

add a new modifier Holy Flames of the Iron Lord
Range units that attack Xarofos while he is in Molten Steel will take 100% more HIT damage and they will lose 175 attack range
(cannot go lower than 250 attack range) and he will no longer lose Armor for his bonus magic and pure resist, all of his Spell will
also do 15% of their damage in Pure while he stay in Molten Steel, If he does stay for 15 seconds in Molten Steel he will gain 35%
Pure Resist and 20% magic resist for 7 seconds, After he stop useing Molten Steel the buff will start to fade away, Also increase
his health regeneration source bonus by 45% but further reduce his mana regeneration by 15% when in Molten Steel.
