SPELL Q Molten KnockUp - Pure -- While in Titan Form
Xarofos will Knockup every enemys near him, dealing medium amount of damage but dealing high damage per seconds to them and reducing
their armor by 50% of Xarofos total armor himself, enemys will also be force to attack him for 1.5 seconds and every time they attack
him for that short duration, they will lose 0.4% of their max health every time. (bosses will lose 0.1% of their max health instead)

