Talent level 40 upgrade Titan Form.
increase duration by 10 seconds
reduce the coldown of both skills by 2
increase the damage of both skills by 30
increase the Strenght scaling for both skills by 10%

add a new modifier Attero Dominatus
Xarofos Will gain a 7 Spell while in Titan Form call Attero Dominatus, Molten KnockUp will reduce the enemys Magic resist by 25% and
make them take 35% increase damage from Pure damage type, Molten KnockUp will also Ignore Magic Immune enemys for the damage and when
they are Magic Immune they will take 100% increase damage from Molten KnockUp, Iron Fist will also deal 5% of Xarofos health in bonus
damage and have 50% more scaling from his Armor as well, the Damage will Become Pure instead of physical and also making the enemys
lose 45 health regeneration for the same duration of the debuff.


Attero Dominatus
Xarofos will Destroy the enemy Mastery, Killing himself in the process but also dealing Extreme Pure Damage to them and reducing their
Armor, Magic resist and their overall damage as well, Xarofos can be Revive by allys but he will gain a Debuff every time that last 240
seconds, Reducing his max health by 75% and attack damage by 100%, he also cannot gain more than 12 16 20 armor and 15% 20% 25% magic
resist for the duration, if he respawn normaly, he doesnt gain this debuff.

base Damage 400 700 1000 plus 400% of Strenght
Max health into Damage 4% 7% 10%
Armor reduce 25 40 55
Magic resist reduce 50% 60% 70%
Overall damage reduce 35% 50% 65%
Coldown 760
Mana cost 85% of max

